n:0 0 10px 10px;\">Au m&ecirc;me titre que le choix des couleurs de son blog, mettre en place un favicon ou un logo fait partie de son identit&eacute; visuelle. A force de partages sur les r&eacute;seaux sociaux, on commence &agrave; vous reconna&icirc;tre. Une uniformit&eacute; dans les symboles et gamme de couleurs qui vous caract&eacute;risent identifieront votre blog WordPress encore ...</p>\n<hr>\n<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://wpformation.com/favicon-wordpress/\">Apprendre &agrave; cr&eacute;er et installer un Favicon pour WordPress</a> est un article de <a title=\"Formation WordPress Ecommerce\" href=\"http://wpformation.com/\">WP Formation</a><br><a href=\"http://wpformation.com/formation-wordpress/\">Formation WordPress</a> &amp; <a href=\"http://wpformation.com/formation-woocommerce-e-commerce/\">WooCommerce</a> - Retrouvez-moi sur <a title=\"Ajouter sur Facebook\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/wpformation\">Facebook</a> - <a title=\"Suivre sur Twitter\" href=\"http://twitter.com/wpformation\">Twitter</a> - <a href=\"http://plus.google.com/+FabriceDucarme/\">Google+</a><br>\n</div>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:4:\"type\";s:4:\"html\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:68:\"\n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n    \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:42:\"WordPress Francophone : WordPress 4.1 RC 1\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:4:\"type\";s:4:\"html\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:2:\"id\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:67:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/WordpressFrancophone/~3/nhnnJdx2rTI/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:2:{s:3:\"rel\";s:9:\"alternate\";s:4:\"href\";s:67:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/WordpressFrancophone/~3/nhnnJdx2rTI/\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:9:\"published\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:25:\"2014-12-14T23:55:59+00:00\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:6:\"author\";a:1:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:1:{s:4:\"name\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"Benoît\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}s:7:\"content\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4732:\"<div>\n<p>WordPress 4.1&nbsp; dans sa premi&egrave;re version Release Candidate est disponible.</p>\n<p>Nous avons r&eacute;alis&eacute; de nombreuses am&eacute;liorations depuis les derni&egrave;res semaines. RC&nbsp; signifie que nous pensons avoir un produit de qualit&eacute;&hellip; mais avec des millions d&rsquo;utilisateurs et des milliers d&rsquo;extensions et th&egrave;mes, il est possible que nous ayons manqu&eacute;s quelques choses. Nous esp&eacute;rons livrer WordPress 4.1 dans sa version finale le 16 d&eacute;cembre prochain. Nous avons besoin de votre aide pour y parvenir. Si vous n&rsquo;avez pas encore testez WP 4.1, maintenant, il est temps ! (S&rsquo;il vous plait, pas sur votre site web en direct, &agrave; moins que vous ne soyez un aventurier !)</p>\n<p><strong>Vous pensez avoir d&eacute;couvert un bug ? </strong>Veuillez le rapporter sur le <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/support/forum/alphabeta/\">forum de </a><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/support/forum/alphabeta/\">support </a><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/support/forum/alphabeta/\">Alpha/Beta</a>. Les bugs connus sont &agrave; d&eacute;couvrir <a href=\"https://core.trac.wordpress.org/report/5\">ici</a>.</p>\n<p>Pour tester WordPress 4.1 RC1, vous pouvez utiliser l&rsquo;extension <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wordpress-beta-tester/\">WordPress Beta Tester</a> ou <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/wordpress-4.1-RC1.zip\">t&eacute;l&eacute;charger la version RC ici</a> (zip). Pour en savoir plus sur WordPress 4.1, visitez la page &laquo;&nbsp;A propos&nbsp;&raquo; dans votre tableau de bord (<strong><img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/core.svn.wordpress.org/branches/3.6/wp-content/themes/twentyten/images/wordpress.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\">&nbsp;&rarr; A propos </strong>dans la barre d&rsquo;outils) ou relisez <a title=\"WordPress 4.1 beta 1\" href=\"http://www.wordpress-fr.net/2014/11/17/wordpress-4-1-beta-1/\">l&rsquo;annonce de la beta</a>.</p>\n<p><strong>D&eacute;veloppeurs</strong>, veuillez tester vos th&egrave;mes et extensions avec WordPress 4.1 et mettez &agrave; jour le &laquo;&nbsp;lisez-moi&nbsp;&raquo; ainsi que la page de votre extension/th&egrave;me sur le r&eacute;pertoire officiel avant la semaine prochaine. Et veuillez rapporter tout probl&egrave;me de compatibilit&eacute;.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/\">Suivez le blog de d&eacute;veloppement du core</a>, o&ugrave; nous publions les <a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/tag/4-1-dev-notes/\">notes pour d&eacute;veloppeurs</a> (Par exemple : si vous cr&eacute;&eacute; un th&egrave;me enfants pour Twenty Fifteen, de nouvelles fonctions de pagination ont &eacute;t&eacute; ajout&eacute;es pour plus de clart&eacute;.</p>\n<p>Veuillez noter que la traduction fran&ccedil;aise peut &ecirc;tre test&eacute;e aussi :</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" width=\"550\">\n<p>T&eacute;l&eacute;chargez la RC1 de WP 4.1 : <a href=\"https://t.co/d9D6PCHTTW\">https://t.co/d9D6PCHTTW</a> Pour tester vos th&egrave;mes, vos extensions&hellip; et relire la traduction fran&ccedil;aise ! <img src=\"http://www.wordpress-fr.net/wp-includes/images/smilies/icon_smile.gif\" alt=\":)\" class=\"wp-smiley\"></p>\n<p>&mdash; WordPressFrancophone (@wordpress_fr) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/wordpress_fr/status/543420787034959872\">December 12, 2014</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p><em>Testez quatre point un</em><br><em>Pourquoi sommes-nous pr&eacute;sent &agrave; cette heure ?</em><br>\nLe <em>Code est po&eacute;sie !<br></em></p>\n<p><em><strong>NB : Adaptation de l&rsquo;article original de <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/news/2014/12/wordpress-4-1-release-candidate/\">wordpress.org</a> (en).</strong></em></p>\n<div class=\"feedflare\">\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?a=nhnnJdx2rTI:WA6B1ap_TvU:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\"></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?a=nhnnJdx2rTI:WA6B1ap_TvU:V_sGLiPBpWU\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?i=nhnnJdx2rTI:WA6B1ap_TvU:V_sGLiPBpWU\" border=\"0\"></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?a=nhnnJdx2rTI:WA6B1ap_TvU:qj6IDK7rITs\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?d=qj6IDK7rITs\" border=\"0\"></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?a=nhnnJdx2rTI:WA6B1ap_TvU:gIN9vFwOqvQ\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?i=nhnnJdx2rTI:WA6B1ap_TvU:gIN9vFwOqvQ\" border=\"0\"></a>\n</div>\n<img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/WordpressFrancophone/~4/nhnnJdx2rTI\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\">\n</div>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:4:\"type\";s:4:\"html\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:6;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:68:\"\n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n    \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:72:\"WordPress Channel : Définir une URL d’archive d’un Custom Post Type\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:4:\"type\";s:4:\"html\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:2:\"id\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:50:\"http://wpchannel.com/url-archive-custom-post-type/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:2:{s:3:\"rel\";s:9:\"alternate\";s:4:\"href\";s:50:\"http://wpchannel.com/url-archive-custom-post-type/\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:9:\"published\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:25:\"2014-12-14T16:30:25+00:00\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:6:\"author\";a:1:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:1:{s:4:\"name\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"Aurélien Denis\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}s:7:\"content\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:868:\"<div>\n<p>Un type de contenu personnalis&eacute; ou custom post type autorise la r&eacute;&eacute;criture d&rsquo;URL afin d&rsquo;internationaliser mais surtout de personnaliser vos slugs &agrave; des fins SEO. Mais saviez-vous que l&rsquo;URL de la page d&rsquo;archive pouvait faire l&rsquo;objet, elle aussi, d&rsquo;une r&eacute;&eacute;criture ?&nbsp; Il arrive parfois que certaines fonctions pourtant utilis&eacute;es au quotidien nous r&eacute;v&egrave;lent encore des&hellip;</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://wpchannel.com/author/aurelien-denis/\">Aur&eacute;lien Denis</a> - <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://wpchannel.com/\">WordPress Channel - Tutoriels, th&egrave;mes &amp; plugins WordPress</a> - <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://wpchannel.com/url-archive-custom-post-type/\">D&eacute;finir une URL d&rsquo;archive d&rsquo;un Custom Post Type</a></p>\n</div>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:4:\"type\";s:4:\"html\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:7;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:68:\"\n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n    \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:50:\"L\'écho des plugins WordPress : Modular Custom CSS\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:4:\"type\";s:4:\"html\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:2:\"id\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:62:\"http://www.echodesplugins.li-an.fr/plugins/modular-custom-css/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:2:{s:3:\"rel\";s:9:\"alternate\";s:4:\"href\";s:62:\"http://www.echodesplugins.li-an.fr/plugins/modular-custom-css/\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:9:\"published\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:25:\"2014-12-13T10:25:46+00:00\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:6:\"author\";a:1:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:1:{s:4:\"name\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5:\"Li-An\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}s:7:\"content\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:69:\"<div>Personnaliser du CSS ind&eacute;pendamment du th&egrave;me</div>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:4:\"type\";s:4:\"html\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:8;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:68:\"\n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n    \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:70:\"WP Formation : Abonnements et paiements récurrents avec Subscriptions\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:4:\"type\";s:4:\"html\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:2:\"id\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:66:\"http://wpformation.com/abonnements-plugin-wordpress-subscriptions/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:2:{s:3:\"rel\";s:9:\"alternate\";s:4:\"href\";s:66:\"http://wpformation.com/abonnements-plugin-wordpress-subscriptions/\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:9:\"published\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:25:\"2014-12-10T08:00:06+00:00\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:6:\"author\";a:1:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:1:{s:4:\"name\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"WPFormation\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}s:7:\"content\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1243:\"<div>\n<p><img width=\"300\" height=\"148\" src=\"http://wpformation.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/subscriptions-woocommerce-abonnement-300x148.jpg\" class=\"attachment-medium wp-post-image\" alt=\"subscriptions-woocommerce-abonnement\" style=\"float: right; margin:0 0 10px 10px;\">Avec WooCommerce Subscriptions, il est tr&egrave;s facile de cr&eacute;er et de g&eacute;rer des produits avec paiements r&eacute;currents sous WordPress. Vous pouvez ainsi cr&eacute;er un produit avec abonnement comme n\'importe quel autre produit de WooCommerce.</p>\n<hr>\n<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://wpformation.com/abonnements-plugin-wordpress-subscriptions/\">Abonnements et paiements r&eacute;currents avec Subscriptions</a> est un article de <a title=\"Formation WordPress Ecommerce\" href=\"http://wpformation.com/\">WP Formation</a><br><a href=\"http://wpformation.com/formation-wordpress/\">Formation WordPress</a> &amp; <a href=\"http://wpformation.com/formation-woocommerce-e-commerce/\">WooCommerce</a> - Retrouvez-moi sur <a title=\"Ajouter sur Facebook\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/wpformation\">Facebook</a> - <a title=\"Suivre sur Twitter\" href=\"http://twitter.com/wpformation\">Twitter</a> - <a href=\"http://plus.google.com/+FabriceDucarme/\">Google+</a><br>\n</div>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:4:\"type\";s:4:\"html\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:9;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:68:\"\n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n    \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:68:\"WordPress Channel : Lister les articles d’un auteur sous WordPress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:4:\"type\";s:4:\"html\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:2:\"id\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:54:\"http://wpchannel.com/lister-articles-auteur-wordpress/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:2:{s:3:\"rel\";s:9:\"alternate\";s:4:\"href\";s:54:\"http://wpchannel.com/lister-articles-auteur-wordpress/\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:9:\"published\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:25:\"2014-12-09T18:35:21+00:00\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:6:\"author\";a:1:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:1:{s:4:\"name\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Mylène Boyrie\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}s:7:\"content\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:752:\"<div>\n<p>Il y a quelques temps, dans les commentaires de l&rsquo;article 8 plugins pour g&eacute;rer votre webzine WordPress, me fut pos&eacute;e la question suivante : Je suis &agrave; la recherche d&rsquo;un plugin pour pouvoir afficher les articles d&rsquo;un m&ecirc;me auteur sur une page ou un article. Je r&eacute;pondis que je n&rsquo;utilisais pas un plugin &agrave; cet&hellip;</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://wpchannel.com/author/mylene/\">Myl&egrave;ne Boyrie</a> - <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://wpchannel.com/\">WordPress Channel - Tutoriels, th&egrave;mes &amp; plugins WordPress</a> - <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://wpchannel.com/lister-articles-auteur-wordpress/\">Lister les articles d&rsquo;un auteur sous WordPress</a></p>\n</div>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:4:\"type\";s:4:\"html\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:10;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:68:\"\n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n    \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:34:\"SEOMix : WP Tech : on recommence ?\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:4:\"type\";s:4:\"html\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:2:\"id\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:40:\"http://www.seomix.fr/wp-tech-recommence/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:2:{s:3:\"rel\";s:9:\"alternate\";s:4:\"href\";s:40:\"http://www.seomix.fr/wp-tech-recommence/\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:9:\"published\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:25:\"2014-12-09T08:00:56+00:00\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:6:\"author\";a:1:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:1:{s:4:\"name\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Daniel Roch\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}s:7:\"content\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2250:\"<div>Retour sur la 1&egrave;re &eacute;dition du WP Tech 2014, et notamment sur les r&eacute;ussites de la journ&eacute;e, les joies de l\'organisation et la probl&eacute;matique des WordCamps. Et vous, cela vous tente un WP Tech 2015 ?\n  <p><strong>Acc&eacute;dez &agrave; l\'article original :</strong> <a href=\"http://www.seomix.fr/wp-tech-recommence/\">WP Tech : on recommence ?</a>.</p>\n<div><img width=\"250\" height=\"250\" src=\"http://www.seomix.fr/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/amphi-wptech-2014-250x250.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumb-250-250-true wp-post-image\" alt=\"Amphi WP Tech 2014\"></div>\n  <p><strong>Voici le d&eacute;but du contenu :</strong> A mon tour &eacute;galement de faire un retour d&rsquo;exp&eacute;rience sur le WP Tech 2014. Le concept Pour ceux qui ne le savent pas, j&rsquo;ai organis&eacute; avec 3 autres personnes la 1&egrave;re &eacute;dition du WP Tech &agrave; Nantes le 29 Novembre dernier (avec Willy Bahuaud, Simon Janin et St&eacute;phanie Vachon). Il s&rsquo;agissait du premier &eacute;v&egrave;nement fran&ccedil;ais ax&eacute; sur les aspects techniques de WordPress. 140 personnes &eacute;taient pr&eacute;sentes, avec pas moins de 12 orateurs diff&eacute;rents sur une journ&eacute;e. Il y avait du monde au WP Tech &laquo;&nbsp;&Eacute;puisant&nbsp;&raquo; est le premier terme qui me vient en t&ecirc;te quand je repense &agrave; cette journ&eacute;e, le second est &laquo;&nbsp;encourageant&nbsp;&raquo;, et le troisi&egrave;me est tout simplement &laquo;&nbsp;Merci&nbsp;&raquo;. La 1&egrave;re &eacute;dition &eacute;tait loin d&rsquo;&ecirc;tre parfaite. On a eu quelques petits d&eacute;fauts et couacs, notamment la vid&eacute;o ou encore le manque de Cookies le midi (bande de gros mangeurs). Mais dans l&rsquo;ensemble, les retours sont vraiments positifs, et cela fait tr&egrave;s plaisir de voir que notre &eacute;v&egrave;nement a su trouver tout de suite son public. Mais je ne suis pas l&agrave; pour vous faire un &eacute;ni&egrave;me retour sur la journ&eacute;e en elle-m&ecirc;me. Si vous voulez un retour officiel, lisez notre article officiel sur le bilan du WP Tech&hellip;</p>\n<hr>\n<img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/seomix-wordpress/~4/w1OBpH6pN2M\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\">\n</div>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:4:\"type\";s:4:\"html\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:11;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:68:\"\n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n    \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:104:\"WordPress Francophone : L’Hebdo WordPress n°247 : WordPress 4.1 – BuddyPress – Meetup Montpellier\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:4:\"type\";s:4:\"html\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:2:\"id\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:67:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/WordpressFrancophone/~3/OpwsDWuoAxw/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:2:{s:3:\"rel\";s:9:\"alternate\";s:4:\"href\";s:67:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/WordpressFrancophone/~3/OpwsDWuoAxw/\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:9:\"published\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:25:\"2014-12-09T07:22:45+00:00\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:6:\"author\";a:1:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:1:{s:4:\"name\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"Benoît\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}s:7:\"content\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2784:\"<div>\n<h3>WordPress 4.1 : des nouveaux template tags</h3>\n<p>L&rsquo;arriv&eacute;e de Twenty Fifteen avec la prochaine version de WordPress 4.1 apporte son lot de nouveaut&eacute; dans les template tags. <a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2014/12/04/new-template-tags-in-4-1/\">Konstantin &eacute;voque tout cela en d&eacute;tail </a>(en).</p>\n<h3>BuddyPress et les post types</h3>\n<p>iMath explique l&rsquo;<a href=\"https://bpdevel.wordpress.com/2014/12/04/about-post-types-and-buddypress-activities/\">int&eacute;gration des post types </a>dans BuddyPress (en).</p>\n<h3>Meetup WordPress &agrave; Montpellier</h3>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.meetup.com/WordPress-Meetup-Montpellier/\">Un premier meetup WordPress</a> va voir le jour en Languedoc-Roussillon d&egrave;s le mois de f&eacute;vrier 2015. Il aura lieu &agrave; Montpellier et est organis&eacute; par Fabrice Ducarme.</p>\n<h3>Wp Tech vous dit merci</h3>\n<p>Le WP Tech a &eacute;t&eacute; un grand succ&egrave;s.<a href=\"http://2014.wptech.fr/merci/\"> Les organisateurs remercient tous les acteurs </a>qui ont permis cette r&eacute;ussite.</p>\n<h3>100 ressources WordPress par cat&eacute;gorie</h3>\n<p>Si vous vouliez <a href=\"http://dailytekk.com/2014/12/08/the-100-best-wordpress-resources-for-2015-categorized-expert-tips/\">des ressources pour WordPress </a>pour lancer l&rsquo;ann&eacute;e 2015, c&rsquo;est ici que vous pouvez commenc&eacute; ! (en)</p>\n<h3>Thierry est pass&eacute; &agrave; la Marmite</h3>\n<p>Pour son 9e Podcast Alex de WPMarmite interroge <a href=\"http://wpmarmite.com/pat-episode-009/\">Thierry Pigot</a>.</p>\n<h3>Pourquoi utiliser Mailchimp ?</h3>\n<p><a href=\"http://wpformation.com/pourquoi-utiliser-le-plugin-mailchimp-avec-wordpress/\">C&rsquo;est la question que se pose S&eacute;bastien Pierrepack </a>sur WPFormation.</p>\n<div class=\"feedflare\">\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?a=OpwsDWuoAxw:VjMKP94_UKk:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\"></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?a=OpwsDWuoAxw:VjMKP94_UKk:V_sGLiPBpWU\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?i=OpwsDWuoAxw:VjMKP94_UKk:V_sGLiPBpWU\" border=\"0\"></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?a=OpwsDWuoAxw:VjMKP94_UKk:qj6IDK7rITs\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?d=qj6IDK7rITs\" border=\"0\"></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?a=OpwsDWuoAxw:VjMKP94_UKk:gIN9vFwOqvQ\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?i=OpwsDWuoAxw:VjMKP94_UKk:gIN9vFwOqvQ\" border=\"0\"></a>\n</div>\n<img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/WordpressFrancophone/~4/OpwsDWuoAxw\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\">\n</div>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:4:\"type\";s:4:\"html\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:12;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:68:\"\n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n    \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:70:\"WP Formation : Pourquoi utiliser le plugin Mailchimp avec WordPress ?\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:4:\"type\";s:4:\"html\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:2:\"id\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:76:\"http://wpformation.com/pourquoi-utiliser-le-plugin-mailchimp-avec-wordpress/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:2:{s:3:\"rel\";s:9:\"alternate\";s:4:\"href\";s:76:\"http://wpformation.com/pourquoi-utiliser-le-plugin-mailchimp-avec-wordpress/\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:9:\"published\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4: