ded I also wanted to share my love for  my native language by offering French tutoring services. I provide my lessons through Skype from Monday to Friday and I ensure to give you an interactive and enjoyable learning experience. With long years of tutoring experience, I know how to adapt my teaching and methodologies according to the needs of my clients.\n\nOur first session, which usually lasts around 30 minutes, is meant to get acquainted with each other and create a personalized study plan based on your individual requirements, whether you are searching for assistance in learning the language from the beginning or just looking for ways to enhance your French language skills. And what’s best about this first session is that it is definitely free!\n\nTake full advantage of our online private tutoring and learn or enhance your language skills in an interactive and convenient way from the comfort of your home.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;','Improve your French Language Skills while sitting on your couch !','','inherit','open','open','','2-autosave-v1','','','2014-11-25 19:00:15','2014-11-25 18:00:15','',2,'http://english.publivision.fr/?p=17',0,'revision','',0),(18,1,'2014-09-22 08:02:16','2014-09-22 07:02:16','','british-107866_640','','inherit','open','open','','british-107866_640','','','2014-09-22 08:02:16','2014-09-22 07:02:16','',2,'http://english.publivision.fr/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/british-107866_640.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(19,1,'2014-09-22 08:02:19','2014-09-22 07:02:19','','converse-enfant-drapeau-uk-british-flag','','inherit','open','open','','converse-enfant-drapeau-uk-british-flag','','','2014-09-22 08:02:19','2014-09-22 07:02:19','',2,'http://english.publivision.fr/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/converse-enfant-drapeau-uk-british-flag.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(21,1,'2014-09-22 08:02:24','2014-09-22 07:02:24','','england-152143_640','','inherit','open','open','','england-152143_640','','','2014-09-22 08:02:24','2014-09-22 07:02:24','',2,'