9-22 08:43:37','2014-09-22 07:43:37','',11,'http://english.publivision.fr/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/4871698256_5380440237_z1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(33,1,'2014-09-22 08:44:13','2014-09-22 07:44:13','<a href=\"http://english.publivision.fr/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/4871698256_5380440237_z1.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-29 size-medium aligncenter\" src=\"http://english.publivision.fr/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/4871698256_5380440237_z1-200x300.jpg\" alt=\"SONY DSC\" width=\"200\" height=\"300\" /></a>\r\n\r\nLorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetuer adipiscing elit. Aenean commodo ligula eget dolor. Aenean massa. Cum sociis natoque penatibus et magnis dis parturient montes, nascetur ridiculus mus. Donec quam felis, ultricies nec, pellentesque eu, pretium quis, sem. Nulla consequat massa quis enim. Donec pede justo, fringilla vel, aliquet nec, vulputate eget, arcu. In enim justo, rhoncus ut, imperdiet a, venenatis vitae, justo. Nullam dictum felis eu pede mollis pretium. Integer tincidunt. Cras dapibus. Vivamus elementum semper nisi.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://english.publivision.fr/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/drapeau_francais.jpg\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-15 aligncenter\" src=\"http://english.publivision.fr/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/drapeau_francais-300x186.jpg\" alt=\"drapeau_francais\" width=\"300\" height=\"186\" /></a>\r\n\r\nAenean vulputate eleifend tellus. Aenean leo ligula, porttitor eu, consequat vitae, eleifend ac, enim. Aliquam lorem ante, dapibus in, viverra quis, feugiat a, tellus. Phasellus viverra nulla ut metus varius laoreet. Quisque rutrum. Aenean imperdiet. Etiam ultricies nisi vel augue. Curabitur ullamcorper ultricies nisi. Nam eget dui. Etiam rhoncus. Maecenas tempus, tellus eget condimentum rhoncus, sem quam semper libero, sit amet adipiscing sem neque sed ipsum. Nam quam nunc, blandit vel, luctus pulvinar, hendrerit id, lorem. Maecenas nec odio et ante tincidunt tempus. Donec vitae sapien ut libero venenatis faucibus. Nullam quis ante. Etiam sit amet orci eget eros faucibus tincidunt. Duis leo. Sed fringilla mauris sit amet nibh. Donec sodales sagittis magna. Sed consequat, leo eget bibendum sodales, augue velit cursus nunc,','Qui sommes nous ','','inherit','open','open','','11-revision-v1','','','2014-09-22 08:44:13','2014-09-22 07:44:13','',11,'http://english.publivision.fr/?p=33',0,'revision','',0),(34,1,'2014-09-22 13:57:17','2014-09-22 12:57:17','&nbsp;\r\n<blockquote><a href=\"http://english.publivision.fr/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/england-152143_640.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-21\" src=\"http://english.publivision.fr/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/england-152143_640-300x169.png\" alt=\"england-152143_640\" width=\"300\" height=\"169\" /></a></blockquote>\r\n<strong>Improve your French Language Skills while sitting on your coach!</strong>\r\n\r\nAre you thinking of going to France or other French-speaking countries either for business or for leisure? Do you want to improve your French language skills at an affordable price? Look no further! My reliable and cost effective French tutoring services can certainly make it easier for you to learn the language without hassles and stress.\r\n\r\nFrench is spoken by more than hundred millions of native speakers, has one-hundred ninety millions non-native speakers all over the world and is an official language of twenty-nine countries. This means that you could certainly gain competitive edge once you learn this wonderful language.\r\n\r\nI am a French freelance translator and I have been teaching English for more than 10 years. I will provide my lessons through Skype from Monday to Saturday and I ensure to give you an interactive and enjoyable learning experience. With long years of tutoring experience, I know how to adapt my teaching and methodologies according to the needs of my clients. I have worked with many people and I have assisted them in delivering the highest quality services that will accommodate their unique requirements.\r\n\r\nOur first session is intended to get acquainted with you and create a studying plan to make sure that you get a really personalized service based on your individual requirements, whether you are searching for assistance in learning the language from the beginning or just looking for ways to enhance your French language skills. And what’s best about this first session is that it is definitely free!\r\nTake full advantage of our online private tutoring and learn or enhance your language skills in an interactive and convienient way from the comfort of your home.','Home','','inherit','open','open','','2-revision-v1','','','2014-09-22 13:57:17','2014-09-22 12:57:17','',2,'http://english.publivision.fr/?p=34',0,'revision','',0),(48,1,'2014-10-14 21:59:02','2014-10-14 20:59:02','&nbsp;\r\n\r\nJe propose des cours du lundi au vendredi, entre 9h00 et 19h00.\r\n\r\nSi vous souhaitez réserver une leçon, contactez-moi, à l\'aide du formulaire de contact en bas de page, en n\'oubliant pas de me communiquer les jours et créneaux horaires qui vous intéresseraient. Une fois que nous avons convenu d\'un rendez-vous, vous n\'avez plus qu\'à vous connecter sur Skype à l\'heure dite et je vous appelle !\r\n\r\nLa première session est gratuite mais par la suite chaque session devra être réglée par <a href=\"https://www.paypal.com/fi/webapps/mpp/home\" target=\"_blank\">Paypal</a> <strong>avant</strong> que le cours ne débute. Par ailleurs, en réservant un cours vous reconnaissez avoir pris connaissance des <a title=\"Cours d’anglais: conditions de service\" href=\"http://www.frenchenglishservices.com/cours-danglais-conditions-de-service/\" target=\"_blank\">conditions de service</a>.\r\n\r\n[contact-form-7 id=\"58\" title=\"Formulaire de contact 1\"]\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-18 size-medium\" src=\"http://www.frenchenglishservices.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/british-107866_640-300x211.jpg\" alt=\"british-107866_640\" width=\"300\" height=\"211\" />